## 🐛 Bug Report

<!-- A clear and concise description of what the bug is. -->

Lib version: 4.3.0

## Steps To Reproduce

<!-- The exact steps required to reproduce the issue, ideally with a code example -->

```javascript
const getCellNoteColumnName = (cell: ExcelJS.Cell) => {
    // 获取标注中的列名称
    let columnName;
    try {
        console.log(cell.value);
        console.log(typeof cell.note === 'string' ? '' : cell.note);
        const noteStr =
            typeof cell.note === 'string'
                ? cell.note
                : cell.note.texts?.[0].text;
        const note = JSON.parse(noteStr || '{}');
        columnName = note.columnName;
    } catch (error) {
        consoleLog.error(
            `获取第一行批注error，请检查上个版本excel是否是规范的。（${cell.value}）`,
        );
        console.log(error);
        process.exit();
    }
    if (!columnName) {
        consoleLog.error(
            '列批注不对，缺少columnName，请检查上个版本excel是否是规范的。',
        );
        process.exit();
    }
    return columnName;
};
const translatedXlsx = new ExcelJS.Workbook();
const columnNames = [];
await translatedXlsx.xlsx.readFile(
     path.resolve(translatedFilePath, translatedFileName),
 );
translatedXlsx
        .getWorksheet(1)
        .getRow(1)
        .eachCell((cell) => {
            columnNames.push(getCellNoteColumnName(cell));
        });
console.log(columnNames)
```

## The expected behaviour:

<!-- A clear and concise description of what you expected to happen. -->
cell.note 不应该为空，但是实际打印出来，批注都为空
